metadata.name: Chaimongkol
metadata.description: Another first work that debuted as an artist for the first time. It's work that I have to trade for many things. in order to complete the work and the most complete Whether the decision to quit the job drop from education All that happened during that time was precious time. It is a feeling that will be remembered for a lifetime. How much dedication to a job This piece took 8 months to sculpt.
